</td><td>
 
 
<h3>By Kathryn Harvey<br>
Read by Paula Prentiss</h3>
<P>
<p>In this riveting sequel to <b><I>Butterfly</I></b>, Kathryn Harvey has created a legendary resort high in the mountains
above Palm Springs called Stars.  When you stay at Stars, you are guaranteed the best of everything.  The
best service, the best food, the best sex, and the best revenge.  Stars is the place where Hollywood's elite go
to shed a pound or two, to close a big deal, to pick up the scandalous rumors, to indulge in a dangerous
liaison or to see a secret fantasy come true.



 
