<h3>By Anita Shreve<br>
Read by Gregory Harrison</h3>
<P>
<p>Charles and Sian were sweethearts when they were thirteen years old.  Thirty years later, circumstance brings
them together again and they begin to grapple with issues they never expected to face.  The two lovers
struggle against odds, reaching across a lifetime to reclaim what once they lost.  In so doing they set in motion
a passionate and tumultuous series of events that moves to a shocking conclusion.



 
