<h3>By Sean Breckenridge<br>
Read by Eric Douglas</h3>
<P>
<p>With an incredible feat of electronic fraud, a young executive bankrupts four of his college friends and runs
off with one of their wives.  When the FBI fails to uncover any leads, the four men pack up their laptop
computers and head for Manhattan on the off chance that the couple is still in the States.  Once in the city,
their frenzied search seems fruitless until a credit card charge pinpoints the couple's location.  Hot in pursuit,
the friends race to catch the couple only to discover a devious double-cross.



 
