<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Fysisk resursteori - Inst. rapporter 1995</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>Rapporter 1995</H2>
<PRE><HR>

<TT>95-01 	&quot;Socio-ecological indicators for sustainability&quot;
	C. Azar, J. Holmberg and K. Lindgren.
	January 1995.

95-02	&quot;An environmental Tax-Shift with Indirect Desirable Effects&quot;
	T. K&aring;berger, J. Holmberg and S. Wirsenius.
	January 1995.

95-03	&quot;Discounting and Distributional Considerations in the Context
	of Global Warming&quot;
	C.Azar, T.Sterner
	May 1995.

95-04	&quot;Vad betyder diskontering i samh&auml;llsekonomiska analyser av 
	v&auml;xthuseffekten?&quot;
	C. Azar.
	Februari 1995.
</TT>
95-05	&quot;Defining The Generatioanal Environmental Debt&quot; (Revised)
	C. Azar, J. Holmberg
	March 1995.

95-06	&quot;Synpunkter p&aring; samh&auml;llets materialanv&auml;ndning&quot;
	S. Karlsson
	Februari 1995.

95-07	&quot;Constant quota versus constant effort harvesting&quot;
	C. Azar, K. Lindgren och J. Holmberg.
	Maj 1995.

95-08	&quot;Retrievability and safeguards concerns regarding plutonium in 
	geological repositories&quot;. 
	Johan Swahn.
	Maj 1995.

95-09	&quot;The long term use of nuclear energy: An evaluation using criteria 
	for proliferation resistance and socio-ecologic sustainability&quot;.
	Johan Swahn.
	Juni 1995.

95-10	&quot;Visions of a Sustainable Society (VISS): Images of the Future
	and Actors in Transition&quot;.
	Bernd Hofmaier, Johan Swahn och Charlotta Fr&auml;ndberg.
	Juli 1995.

95-11	&quot;The global requirement of food, materials and energy&quot;.
	G&ouml;ran Berndes och Stefan Wirsenius.
	Augusti 1995.

95-12 &quot;Sustainable use of lead?&quot;.
	Sten Karlsson.
	Augusti 1995.

95-13 &quot;Kan flyg milj&ouml;m&auml;ssigt konkurrera med h&ouml;ghastighetst&aring;g?&quot;.
	Ingrid R&aring;de.
	Juli 1995.

95-14 &quot;Fair Play in the prisoner's Dilemma&quot;.
	Kristian Lindgren.
	September 1995.

95-15 Reviderad rapport nr (94-11)
	&quot;Socio-Ecological Principles For A Sustainable Society&quot;.
	J. Holmberg, K-H. Rob&egrave;rt and K-E. Eriksson.
	October 1995.

95-16 Reviderad rapport nr (95-01)
	&quot;Socio-Ecological indicators for sustainability&quot;
	C. Azar, J. Holmberg and K. Lindgren.
	Oktober 1995

95-17 Prelimin&auml;r version
	&quot;Evolutionary Dynamics in Game-Theoretic Models&quot;
	Kristian Lindgren
	November 1995

95-18 &quot;A Physical system perspective on the societal metabolism and 
	the environmental problems&quot;
	J. Holmberg and S. Karlsson
	December 1995

95-19 &quot;A compass for sustainable development&quot;
	Karl-Henrik Rob&egrave;rt, Herman Daily, Paul Hawken and John Holmberg.
	December 1995</PRE>
