<HEAD>
    <TITLE>INES Congress: Suggested preparation</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>SUGGESTED PREPARATION FOR THE CONGRESS</H2>
Sustainable development is a complex interdisciplinary issue and task. The
Congress organizers extend a strong wish to all participants to prepare
themselves for participation. Everyone will have to choose an appropriate
way. We suggest in particular participation in e-mail discussion lists for
workshop preparation and preparatory reading.<BR>
<BR>
Hartwig Spitzer<BR>
(Chairman of INES) 
<H3><STRONG>E-mail fileserver</STRONG></H3>
There is a <A HREF="emailfileserve.html">fileserver </A>available where
files can be fetched be sending e-mail messages. This can be especialkly
useful for those not having access to these WWW pages. 
<H3>E-mail discussion lists</H3>
The congress <A HREF="emaillists.html">e-mail information and discussion
list</A> is now up and running. 
<H3>Suggested preparatory reading</H3>
There are <A HREF="sources.html">literature and internet resources pages</A>
on these INES Amsterdam congress pages. In addition, the Congress organizers
have a special page for <A HREF="litterature/sugglitt.html">suggested preparatory
reading</A>.<BR>
<BR>
