    <TITLE>INES Congress: Student meeting</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STUDENT MEETING</H2>
<BR>
Knut Aufermann and other student members of INES are trying to build up
a student network of INES. They plan a student meeting on Saturday evening
at the Amsterdam Congress. They have already set up an E-Mail Discussion
List for students to get in contact before the congress <BR>
starts. If you are interested in joining this list please contact<BR>
<BR>
<A HREF="mailto:fiedeler@physnet.uni-hamburg.de">fiedeler@physnet.uni-hamburg.de</A>
or<BR>
<A HREF="mailto:auferman@rz.uni-potsdam.de">auferman@rz.uni-potsdam.de</A><BR>
