<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>INES Congress: Location</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>LOCATION<BR>
<BR>
Registration in Amsterdam will take place in the direct vicinity of the
plenary sessions, i.e., at Singel 411.</H2>
<BR>
The plenary sessions of the congress will be held in the main auditorium
of the University of Amsterdam, Singel 411, in the historical center of
Amsterdam. The workshop and the poster sessions will be held in buildings
of the Faculty of Literature of the University, Spuistraat 134 and 210,
within walking distance of the auditorium.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
