    <TITLE>INES Congress: Registration and fees</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<FORM ACTION="../cgi-bin/Flexmail/Flexmail.acgi" ENCTYPE="x-www-form-encoded"
METHOD="POST">
<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="flexConfig" VALUE="registration.flx">
<H2>REGISTRATION AND FEES</H2>
<H3>|For those interested, approximately 170 persons registered via the
form below, of the 500 partcipants who registered before the Congress started.]</H3>
<BR>
<BR>
Please register before 1 May 1996, preferentially by means of the registration
form attached to this WWW page (<A HREF="#anchor204230">see below</A>),
alternatively by printing the form and faxing or mailing it to the Congress
Secretariat:<BR>
<BR>
Congress Secretariat, <BR>
Mr. Reiner Braun, <BR>
P.O. Box 101707, 44017 Dortmund, Germany<BR>
<BR>
FAX: +49 231 103869<BR>
<BR>
A copy of the registration form in <STRONG>Acrobat Reader</STRONG> or <STRONG>postscript</STRONG>
format for printing can be fetched from the <A HREF="ftp.html">Congress
ftp archives</A>. <BR>
<BR>
To correct or change any information in a previously sent registration,
either via the form below or via mail or fax go to the <A HREF="correction.html">correction
page</A>. 
<H3><BR>
Congress registration fee</H3>
The congress registration fee amounts to: 
<PRE>					 pay before	pay after
  Category 		 		May 1st, 1996  May 1st, 1996

					Hfl 	DM 	Hfl 	DM

1. participants from OECD countries 	135 	120 	200 	180
2. participants from other countries 		40 		60
3. students from OECD countries 	45 	40 	65 	60
4. students from other countries 		10 		15

Carbon dioxide compensation contribution DM 5-30 (self taxation)</PRE>
<BR>
Registration is only effected by paying the fee and after confirmation by
the Congress Secretariat.<BR>
<BR>
Donations for travel support of third world participants are appreciated.
<BR>
<BR>
Participants from the NETHERLANDS pay in dutch currency to Stichting INES-Nederland,
Amsterdam, Postbank account 4506758. <BR>
<BR>
Participants from OTHER EUROPEAN COUNTRIES pay in DM by check to the Congress
Secretariat or by bank draft or money order to Postbank Hamburg, Banc code
200 100 20, account INES no 156 72-207. <BR>
<BR>
Participants from OTHER REGIONS send cheques to Reiner Braun, Congress Secretariat.
Do not send cheques to the Netherlands! <BR>
<BR>
A reduction of the fee is possible in special cases, subject to approval
by Reiner Braun, Congress Secretariat. 
