<HEAD>
    <TITLE>INES Congress: Accommodation</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>ACCOMMODATION</H2>
<BR>
Hotel reservations can be made by filling in the <A HREF="acomform.html">hotel
registration form</A> or by sending the form on page 12 of the program booklet
to: <BR>
<BR>
Netherlands Reservations Centre<BR>
P.B. 404, <BR>
NL-2260 AK Leidschendam<BR>
The Netherlands<BR>
<BR>
Tel: +31 70 3202549, Fax: +31 70 3204237<BR>
<BR>
All reservations will be made by this office. Prices of low cost hotels
usually do not include breakfast.<BR>
<BR>
Participants who are not familiar with European hotel booking procedures,
may refer to the Congress Secretariat.<BR>
<BR>
If you are interested in camping, here are <A HREF="camping.html">some camping
areas near Amsterdam</A>.<BR>
<BR>
Participants should investigate the possibility of cheap tours to Amsterdam,
including travel and accommodation, offered in their own country. <BR>
<BR>
