<H2>LITTERATURE AND INTERNET RESOURCES PAGES</H2>
<BR>
On these pages the following information and links are presented: 
<UL>
  <LI><A HREF="litterature.html">Litterature on sustainable development</A>.
  <LI>Links to <A HREF="organizations.html">research institutes, governmental
and non-governmental organizations</A> working with issues of concern for
the Congress. 
