of interest</A>. 
</UL>
It is also the ambition that litterature and links will be added on each
workshop page.<BR>
<BR>
The readers of these pages are invited to suggest additional litterature
and links by sending e-mail to Johan Swahn (<A HREF="mailto:frtjs@fy.chalmers.se">frtjs@fy.chalmers.se</A>).<BR>
