<DOCHDR>
http://www.frt.fy.chalmers.se:80/amst/workshops/ws21/ermolenko.html 129.16.119.200 19970210101441 text/html 4798
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/33439
Message-ID: <af244e57.244@g7-mac5.fy.chalmers.se>
