<HEAD>
    <TITLE>INES Workshop: Industry and sustainability (Services)</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>2.3.B Industry and sustainability: Pioneer-industries on sustainable
services</H2>
<BR>
Organised by the <A HREF="http://unep.frw.uva.nl/">UNEP-Working Group on
Sustainable Product Development</A>.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Convenors:</B> <BR>
Jogi Panghaal<BR>
P.O. Box 3213, New Delhi, 110013 India<BR>
TEL: +91 1146 28984, FAX: +91 1146 26699<BR>
E-MAIL: <A HREF="mailto:delaac97@giasdl01.vsnl.net.in">delaac97@giasdl01.vsnl.net.in</A><BR>
<BR>
Ezio Manzini (Italy) , UNEP-WG-SPD<BR>
<BR>
Topic: exploration of research and application of the concept of sustainable
services, in relation to development<BR>
<BR>
