http://www.frt.fy.chalmers.se:80/amst/workshops/ws24/moll.html 129.16.119.200 19970210101733 text/html 4354
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/33439
Message-ID: <af244e57.264@g7-mac5.fy.chalmers.se>
