<DOCNO>WT13-B39-245</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA049-000856-B023-119</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.frt.fy.chalmers.se:80/amst/workshops/ws27/niemczynowicz.html 129.16.119.200 19970210101847 text/html 4187
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
