<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>INES Workshop: Golubov abstract</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>Abstract</H2>
<H3>The ecological outcomes of the underground nuclear explosions and problems
of sustainable development</H3>
Boris Golubov<BR>
Russian Academy of Sciences<BR>
Scientific Secretary Scientific Council on the Problems of the Biosphere<BR>
Narofominskaya st. 2, fl 85, 119619 Moskwa, Rossia<BR>
TEL: +7 095 439 2448, +7 095 124 5388, FAX: +7 095 230 2090<BR>
E-MAIL: <A HREF="mailto:antip@ginran.msk.su">antip@ginran.msk.su</A><BR>
