<TD><IMG SRC="image/globe_p.gif"  BORDER=0>
</TABLE>


<H2><A HREF="info/info_a.htm"><STRONG>Disease Information</STRONG></A></H2>

<P>Emergency reports sent by Member Countries to the Central Bureau of the OIE detailing important epidemiological events are published each week in <A HREF="info/info_a.htm">Disease&nbsp;Information</A>.</P>

<BR>
<H2><A HREF="indemne/fa_a.htm"><STRONG>List of FMD free countries</STRONG></A></H2>
<P>A Resolution was adopted by the International Committee of the OIE on 24 May 1996 entitled "Recognition of the foot and mouth disease status of Member Countries".  The text of this Resolution has been annotated to take into account the recent appearance of this disease in various countries.</P>
