<HEAD>
<TITLE>OIE Overview - Central Bureau</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../image/back.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#6B9F00" VLINK="#006BB4" TEXT="#000000">

<TABLE>
<TR VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><H1>Director General and Central Bureau</H1>
<TD><IMG SRC="../image/globe_p.gif"  BORDER=0>
</TABLE>

<TABLE BORDER=0>
<TR>
<TD>
<P>The Central Bureau, located in Paris, is placed under the authority of the Director General of the OIE, appointed by the International Committee. In 1990, Dr&nbsp;J.&nbsp;Blancou was appointed Director General; his appointement was renewed for a five year period during the 63rd General Session in May 1995. The Central Bureau implements and coordinates information, technical cooperation and scientific activities, which the International Committee has decided upon.</P>
<TD><IMG SRC="../image/immeuble.gif" ALIGN="RIGHT">
</TABLE>
<P>Furthermore, the Central Bureau provides the secretariat for the annual General Session of the Committee, meetings of the Commissions and technical meetings organised at the OIE; assistance is also given by the Central Bureau to the secretariat of regional and specialised conferences.</P>

<HR>
Back to the <A HREF="oie_a.htm">OIE overview</A> or to the <A HREF="../HOME.HTM">OIE home page</A>
