<HEAD>
<TITLE>DISEASE INFORMATION</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../image/back.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#6B9F00" VLINK="#006BB4" TEXT="#000000">
<H2>14 February 1997; Vol. 10 - No. 7
</H2>
<CENTER><STRONG>Contents</STRONG><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=3>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec1">Newcastle disease in the United Kingdom / Northern Ireland</A>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec2">Foot and mouth disease in Bulgaria: the Delegate declares his country free</A>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec3">Classical swine fever in the Netherlands</A>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec4">Newcastle disease in Swaziland</A>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec5">Classical swine fever in Germany</A>
