</EM>
unknown.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
B.	Mode of spread: </STRONG>
</EM>
in one of the farms in Paderborn, contamination was due to human intervention; in the farm in Soest, the virus was introduced through movement of vehicles.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Control measures during reporting period: </STRONG>
</EM>
the remaining animals have been slaughtered and will be destroyed in a rendering plant; ban on the movement of susceptible animals within the area around the infected holdings; tracing of animal movements into and out of the infected holdings.</P>
