<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Nature of diagnosis: </STRONG>
</EM>
clinical, postmortem and laboratory.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Number of cases confirmed since 1 January 1997: </STRONG>
</EM>
one (1).</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
