<H2>17 January 1997; Vol. 10 - No. 3
</H2>
<CENTER><STRONG>Contents</STRONG><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=3>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec1">Newcastle disease in the United Kingdom / Great Britain</A>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec2">Bovine spongiform encephalopathy in France</A>
