<H2>3 January 1997; Vol. 10 - No. 1
</H2>
<CENTER><STRONG>Contents</STRONG><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=3>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec1">Bovine spongiform encephalopathy in France</A>
</TABLE><BR>
</CENTER><CENTER>
<P><STRONG>
