<P><STRONG>
<A NAME="Sec1"></A>NEWCASTLE DISEASE IN DENMARK</P>
</CENTER>
<P></STRONG>
<EM>
Text of a fax received on 23 August 1996 from Dr E. Stougaard, Chief Veterinary Officer, Ministry of Agriculture, Frederiksberg:</P>
<P></EM>
S. R. - 1</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Date of initial detection of animal health incident: </STRONG>
</EM>
1 August 1996.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Estimated date of first infection: </STRONG>
</EM>
August 1996.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Number of separate outbreaks identified so far: </STRONG>
</EM>
two (2).</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Geographical identification of the outbreaks: </P>
<P></STRONG>
</EM>
1/96.	Vester Skerninge, Fyn (F&uuml;nen) county</P>
<P>2/96.	Helsinge, Frederiksborg county.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Details concerning the outbreaks:</P>
