<H2>2 August 1996; Vol. 9 - No. 29
</H2>
<CENTER><STRONG>Contents</STRONG><BR>
<TABLE BORDER=3>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec1">Infectious bovine rhinotracheitis / Infectious pustular vulvovaginitis in Kuwait</A>
<TR><TD><A HREF="#Sec2">Venezuelan equine encephalomyelitis in Mexico</A>
