</TABLE>
</CENTER><STRONG><EM><P>Control measures taken to date: </STRONG>
</EM>
stamping-out policy includes the purchase and destruction of the affected lot of young parrots. Federal and State animal health authorities are currently completing trace back procedures of contact birds with 100% sampling (cloacal swabbing).</P>
