<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Control measures taken to date: </STRONG>
</EM>
Strpce community was declared to be infected and the neighbouring communities to be endangered; the prescribed stringent measures were implemented. All 74 heifers were slaughtered on 10 July 1996 and buried in the prescribed manner; the pasture was disinfected.</P>
