Comments to date concerning epidemiology of the disease: </STRONG>
</EM>
investigations into the cause of the outbreaks are continuing.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Control measures taken during report period: </STRONG>
</EM>
movement restrictions were imposed on all infected farms. Vaccination in some farms was applied using an inactivated virus vaccine. The disease has been made notifiable and a ministerial order will be issued next week. Disinfection of infected premises and control of rodents, wild birds and insects on infected farms.</P>
