Conclusions to date concerning nature of agent: </STRONG>
</EM>
avian paramyxovirus-1, with intracerebral pathogenicity index of 0.9.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Comments to date concerning epidemiology of the disease: </STRONG>
</EM>
infection from feral pigeons.</P>
<P><STRONG>
<EM>
Control measures taken during report period: </STRONG>
</EM>
area restrictions on movements of all birds; inspection of all premises with poultry within 3km of the infected place.</P>
